        &nbsp;<a href="post.asp?method=ReplyQuote&amp;REPLY_ID=38658&amp;TOPIC_ID=4872&amp;FORUM_ID=2&amp;CAT_ID=1&amp;Forum_Title=General+Discussions&amp;Topic_Title=Hybrid+cast+time+reduction+%2D+Why%3F&amp;M="><img src="icon_reply_topic.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Reply with Quote" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>

        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         I think logical answers include 1) its needed for gameplay as they are being pounded on and harder for them to channel and 2) they are casting lower level spells than you are in general.</P><P>Arguments though would include 1) they are getting pounded on so it SHOULD be harder for them to channel through and 2) so shouldn't MY cast times decrease as I level up?</P><P><<>><<>><<>><<>><<>><<>><<>><<>><<>><<>><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=168712" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=168712</a><BR><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
      </tr>

