         Try casting all your spells while being slammed on by mobs, I played a SK to 55 and not only do they have low mana but the spells they get are not very good for the level they get them. Until 55 your best life tap does 75 pts, its barely worth the cast time since you can do far more during the cast time with your weapon. BTW I know they get a 280 pt tap at 49 but its recast is like 2 minutes and takes a ton of mana.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
